\par\pard\plain \li400\ri400\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Though Abraham\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s circumstances were different from ours, we can learn important lessons from him as to the kind of faith God expects from us today. He shows us \u8220\'93what it means to believe\u8221\'94 (Schlatter, 114).}
