\par\pard\plain \li400\fi360\ri400\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Abraham\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s hope was focused especially on the promise of countless descendants as recorded in }{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosref/Bible.Ge15.5"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf3 Gen 15:5}}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 . After calling his attention to the multitude of stars in the heavens, God said to him, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93So shall your offspring be.\u8221\'94 At this time Abraham was between 75 and 86 years old (}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosref/Bible.Ge12.4"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf3 Gen 12:4}}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 ; }{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosref/Bible.Ge16.16"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf3 16:16}}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 ), and was already very conscious of the fact that he was still childless (}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosref/Bible.Ge15.2-3"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf3 Gen 15:2\endash 3}}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 ). But God reassured him, and Abraham believed (}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosref/Bible.Ge15.6"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf3 Gen 15:6}}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 ). }
