\par\pard\plain \li400\ri400\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Certainly no one\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s faith, not even Abraham\u8217\'92s, is perfect. But \u8220\'93despite his spiritual imperfection, Abraham always came back to the Lord in faith, and the Lord honored that faith and continued to renew his promises to Abraham\u8221\'94 (MacArthur, I:}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosres/rommntc?ref=Page.p+237"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf3 237}}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 ).}
