\par\pard\plain \li400\ri400\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 With it the idea would be that his faith was so strong that he did not pay any attention to the fact that he and Sarah appeared to be past the age of natural childbearing. He did not regard that as the deciding factor, and he did not allow it to weaken his faith (Lard, 147). All that mattered was God\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s promise.}
