\par\pard\plain \li400\ri400\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 In fact, says Paul, the key words in }{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosref/Bible.Ge15.6"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf3 Gen 15:6}}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  were included in the Bible specifically for our sakes. }{\f1\fs24\b1\i0 The words \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93it was credited to him\u8221\'94 were written not for him alone, but also for us.\u8230\'85}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  The whole account of Abraham and the record of his strong faith were written not just to honor him but to benefit us believers today.}
