\par\pard\plain \li400\ri400\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The key words of }{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosref/Bible.Ge15.6"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf3 Gen 15:6}}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 , \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93it was credited to him as righteousness,\u8221\'94 mean simply that he was }{\f2\fs24\b0\i1 justified}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 by his faith. This sets the pattern for those today }{\f1\fs24\b1\i0 to whom God will credit righteousness}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 , i.e., whom God will justify. And of whom is this blessed category comprised?\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8230\'85 }{\f1\fs24\b1\i0 us who believe in him who raised Jesus our Lord from the dead.\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8230\'85}
