\par\pard\plain \li400\ri400\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Paul fittingly closes this chapter with a brief summary of the gospel facts that make salvation by grace possible and that are at the very heart of justifying faith: the death and resurrection of Jesus (see }{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosref/Bible.1Co15.1-4"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf3 1 Cor 15:1\endash 4}}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 ): }{\f1\fs24\b1\i0 He was delivered over to death for our sins and was raised to life for our justification}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 .}
